<resources>
    <!-- COLOR NAMING CONVENTION:
         - Colors ending in _dark (e.g., text_primary_dark) are ADAPTIVE:
           dark values in light mode, light values in dark mode via values-night override.
         - Colors ending in _light (e.g., background_light, card_background_light)
           are also ADAPTIVE: light in light mode, dark in dark mode via values-night override.
         - Colors WITHOUT these suffixes (e.g., text_primary, background, surface)
           are NON-ADAPTIVE and always resolve to the same value regardless of theme.
    -->

